author: fruboes
body: New filters for FSQ jet triggers. For singjle/double jet FSQ paths we need to be able to specify eta ranges (lower/higher edge). Current filters allow to specify only one edge or in case of CandViewSelectors (where cut is definied via string parsed by EspressionParser) do not support writing to the triggerEvent (which makes trigger offline DQM compilcated)
title: New fsq jet filtes 74x 20150120 0200
